page.title: 12AN INTERVIEW
page.content: WE INTERVIEWED A LADY WHO WAS A HOUSE WIFE IN WOOTTON ST LAWRENCE. SHE SAID THAT SHE REALLY LIKES THE VILLAGE.SOMETIMES SHE WOULD GO NEXT DOOR AND TALK TO HER FRIEND. BEFORE SHE LIVED IN THE COTTAGE SHE LIVED DOWN THE ROAD.THE LADY SAID THAT THERE ARE NO CLUBS AROUND HERE. HER MAIN HOBBY IS HORSE RIDING AND SHE SAID THAT SHE REALLY ENJOYS IT. SHE AISO SAID THAT SHE DOESNT OWN ANY FARM LAND. SHE SAID THAT SHE HAS LIVED IN THE VILLAGE FOR FOUR YEARS.SHE SAID THAT SHE WONT MOVE YET BECAUSE SHE LIKES IT HERE.SHE SAID THAT THE COTTAGE WAS BUILT IN 1940 AND SHE LIKES THE COTTAGE A LOT.
